title: Sales of Ironing Machines for United States
notes:
Data Cover Manufacturers' Sales Of Electric And Gas Heated Ironers To Wholesalers, Distributors, And Dealers. Reports To The American Washer And Ironer Manufacturers Association Cover 98% Of The Industry And Have Been Raised To Complete Coverage. Source: Survey Of Current Business, October 1939, P. 17; January 1940, P. 51

This NBER data series m06037 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 6 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter06.html.
